import { useStyles } from "./styles";
import { Grid, Typography } from '@material-ui/core';

function Stats({ planet }) {
    const classes = useStyles();

    return (
        <>
            <Grid container>
                <Grid item sm={12} md={3} spacing={3}>
                    <Typography>
                        rotation time
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography>
                        {planet.map(el => el.rotation)}
                    </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item sm={12} md={3} spacing={3}>
                    <Typography>

                    </Typography>
                    <Typography>
                        
                    </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item sm={12} md={3} spacing={3}>
                    <Typography>

                    </Typography>
                    <Typography>
                        
                    </Typography>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item sm={12} md={3} spacing={3}>
                    <Typography>

                    </Typography>
                    <Typography>
                        
                    </Typography>
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
        </>
    )
}

export default Stats
